---
layout: base.njk
title: SERRE Studio
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <img class="hero-symbol" src="/assets/serre-symbol.png" alt="SERRE Studio symbol">
    <p class="eyebrow">Visual Archive · Research · Exhibition</p>
    <h1>SERRE Studio</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
    <a class="text-link" href="/archive/">Enter Archive <span>→</span></a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-image"><img src="/assets/hero-gallery.png" alt="조용한 전시 공간" loading="eager"></div>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Curated Collections</p>
    <h2>전시와 연구를 천천히 둘러보세요.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="category-grid">
    <a href="/archive/"><img src="/assets/home/category-exhibition.png" alt=""><span>Archive</span></a>
    <a href="/visual-dictionary/"><img src="/assets/home/category-dictionary.png" alt=""><span>Visual Dictionary</span></a>
    <a href="/research-notes/"><img src="/assets/home/category-cinematic.png" alt=""><span>Research Notes</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.publicExhibitions.length %}
<section class="home-section">
  <div class="section-heading"><p class="eyebrow">Recent Exhibition</p><h2>최근 전시</h2></div>
  <div class="archive-grid">
    {% for item in collections.publicExhibitions | slice(0, 4) %}{% include "card.njk" %}{% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
